s="horizontal-scroll-wrapper"><div class="table-block-component"><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><table-block _nghost-ng-c1601480523="" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1601480523="" class="table-block has-export-button new-table-style is-at-scroll-start is-at-scroll-end"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1601480523="" not-end-of-paragraph="" class="table-content not-end-of-paragraph" jslog="275421;track:impression,attention" data-hveid="5"><table data-path-to-node="4"><thead><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="4,0,0,0">Variable</span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="4,0,1,0">Color</span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="4,0,2,0">Code Meaning</span></td></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="4,1,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,1,0,0" data-index-in-node="0"><code data-path-to-node="4,1,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">G</code></b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="4,1,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Green</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="4,1,2,0"><code data-path-to-node="4,1,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">0;32</code> (Normal Green)</span></td></tr><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="4,2,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,2,0,0" data-index-in-node="0"><code data-path-to-node="4,2,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">R</code></b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="4,2,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,2,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Red</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="4,2,2,0"><code data-path-to-node="4,2,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">0;31</code> (Normal Red)</span></td></tr><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="4,3,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,3,0,0" data-index-in-node="0"><code data-path-to-node="4,3,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Y</code></b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="4,3,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,3,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Yellow</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="4,3,2,0"><code data-path-to-node="4,3,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">1;33</code> (Bold/Bright Yellow)</span></td></tr><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="4,4,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,4,0,0" data-index-in-node="0"><code data-path-to-node="4,4,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">N</code></b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="4,4,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,4,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Normal</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="4,4,2,0"><code data-path-to-node="4,4,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">0</code> (Resets everything back to default)</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1601480523="" hide-from-message-actions="" class="table-footer hide-from-message-actions"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c1601480523="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copy table" aria-label="Copy table" data-test-id="copy-table-button" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="276666;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_2c672f0936927d16&quot;,&quot;c_ef6aa1271e501096&quot;,null,null,null,null,null,null,1,null,null,null,0]]"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1601480523="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-l google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----></div></div><!----></table-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element></div></div><hr data-path-to-node="5"><h3 data-path-to-node="6">How the code works</h3><p data-path-to-node="7">If you look at a sequence like <code data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="31">\033[0;32m</code>:</p><ul data-path-to-node="8"><li><p data-path-to-node="8,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="8,0,0" data-index-in-node="0"><code data-path-to-node="8,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">\033</code></b>: This is the <b data-path-to-node="8,0,0" data-index-in-node="18">Escape character</b> (it signals a command is coming).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="8,1,0" data-index-in-node="0"><code data-path-to-node="8,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">[</code></b>: The Control Sequence Introducer.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="8,2,0" data-index-in-node="0"><code data-path-to-node="8,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">0;32</code></b>: The actual "instruction." <code data-path-to-node="8,2,0" data-index-in-node="32">0</code> means normal text, and <code data-path-to-node="8,2,0" data-index-in-node="57">32</code> is the code for Green.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,3,0"><b data-path-to-node="8,3,0" data-index-in-node="0"><code data-path-to-node="8,3,0" data-index-in-node="0">m</code></b>: The character that finishes the sequence.</p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node="9">Why the <code data-path-to-node="9" data-index-in-node="8">N</code> variable is so important</h3><p data-path-to-node="10">Without the <b data-path-to-node="10" data-index-in-node="12"><code data-path-to-node="10" data-index-in-node="12">N</code> (Reset)</b> at the end, your entire terminal would stay that color forever! Usually, people use them like this in a script:</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c2432481757="" class="ng-tns-c2432481757-15 ng-s